      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5652430/" class="title-link">民主的细节</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5652430"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/thisislaoxu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u40209076-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/thisislaoxu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">西雅图之声</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-11-13"
      class="main-meta">2012-11-13 10:50:20</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5652430_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  最近贵党在开一个内部会议，其实也不能说“在开”，实际上已经开过会了，现在相当于拿录播冒充直播，摆出全国同步跟着开会的架势来。  开会是好事，英文叫conference，con是一起的意思，fer是拿来的意思，ence没意思，是名词后缀，意思显而易见，大伙儿把意见都拿到一桌上，看...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5652430/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">15有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
